overview: When Longfellow Deeds, a small-town pizzeria owner and poet, inherits $40 billion from his deceased uncle, he quickly begins rolling in a different kind of dough. Babe, a television tabloid reporter, poses as an innocent small-town girl to do an exposé on Deeds.
title: Mr. Deeds
production_companies: Columbia Pictures, New Line Cinema, Happy Madison Productions, Out of the Blue... Entertainment
tagline: Don't let the fancy clothes fool you.

overview: During the last days of World War II, Germany, desperate for any last grasp to defeat the allied powers, looked to their last remaining weapons and soldiers. The German Navy and the last remaining U-Boats were formed together for one desperate last mission – a mission to attack the United States Homeland, known as Operation Seawolf. Captain Hans Kessler, a grizzled submarine commander from both World Wars, is called into service to make one mission a success and help turn the tide of the war.
title: Operation Seawolf
production_companies: Relis Pic
tagline: Last mission to win this war.

overview: Two estranged brothers reunite at their childhood home in the Alaskan wild. They set out on a two-day hike and are stalked by an unrelenting grizzly bear.
title: Into the Grizzly Maze
production_companies: Purple Pictures, Indomitable Entertainment, Paul Schiff Productions
tagline: Hunt or be hunted.

overview: Two FBI agents investigating the murder of civil rights workers during the 60s seek to breach the conspiracy of silence in a small Southern town where segregation divides black and white. The younger agent trained in FBI school runs up against the small town ways of his partner, a former sheriff.
title: Mississippi Burning
production_companies: Orion Pictures
tagline: 1964. When America was at war with itself.

overview: Four high school teachers launch a drinking experiment: upholding a constant low level of intoxication.
title: Another Round
production_companies: Zentropa Entertainments, Film i Väst, Topkapi Films, Zentropa International Sweden, Zentropa International Netherlands

overview: Two crew members wake up on an abandoned spacecraft with no idea who they are, how long they've been asleep, or what their mission is. The two soon discover they're actually not alone – and the reality of their situation is more horrifying than they could have imagined.
title: Pandorum
genres: Action, Horror, Mystery, Science Fiction, Thriller
production_companies: Impact Pictures, Studio Babelsberg, Summit Entertainment, Constantin Film, Overture Films
production_countries: Germany, United Kingdom, United States of America
tagline: Don't fear the end of the world. Fear what happens next.

overview: A neurotic worker ant in love with a rebellious princess rises to unlikely stardom when he switches places with a soldier. Signing up to march in a parade, he ends up under the command of a bloodthirsty general. But he's actually been enlisted to fight against a termite army.
title: Antz
production_companies: Pacific Data Images, DreamWorks Animation, DreamWorks Pictures
tagline: Every ant has his day.

overview: Ryo Morinaka is a university student and works part-time at a bar. He is bored with his daily life and exists in a state of torpor. One day, his friend Shinya Tajima brings the owner of a host bar over to the place where Ryo Morinaka works. Shizuka Mido is the owner of the host bar. Soon, Ryo Morinaka begins to work for Shizuka Mido at the members only host bar. He feels embarrassment initially, but he fulfills the desires of women and develops a sense of purpose.
title: Call Boy
production_companies: Phantom Film

overview: The quiet family life of Nels Coxman, a snowplow driver, is upended after his son's murder. Nels begins a vengeful hunt for Viking, the drug lord he holds responsible for the killing, eliminating Viking's associates one by one. As Nels draws closer to Viking, his actions bring even more unexpected and violent consequences, as he proves that revenge is all in the execution.
title: Cold Pursuit
production_companies: StudioCanal, Paradox Produksjon, MAS Productions, Summit Entertainment, Disappearance, Canal+, Ciné+
production_countries: Canada, France, Norway, United Kingdom, United States of America
tagline: Meet Nels Coxman. Citizen of the Year.

overview: The murder of her father sends a teenage tomboy on a mission of 'justice', which involves avenging her father's death. She recruits a tough old marshal, 'Rooster' Cogburn because he has 'true grit', and a reputation of getting the job done.
title: True Grit
production_companies: Wallis-Hazen Inc., Paramount Pictures
tagline: The strangest trio ever to track a killer.

overview: A love story about chance meetings, instant attractions, and casual betrayals. Four strangers - with one thing in common: each other.
title: Closer
production_companies: Columbia Pictures, Inside Track
production_countries: United Kingdom, United States of America
tagline: If you believe in love at first sight, you never stop looking.

overview: Just when you thought it was safe to sleep, Freddy Krueger returns in this sixth installment of the Nightmare on Elm Street films, as psychologist Maggie Burroughs, tormented by recurring nightmares, meets a patient with the same horrific dreams. Their quest for answers leads to a certain house on Elm Street -- where the nightmares become reality.
title: Freddy's Dead: The Final Nightmare
production_companies: New Line Cinema
tagline: They saved the best for last.

overview: Against the vibrant backdrop of a 1960s-inspired, retro-futuristic world, Marvel's First Family is forced to balance their roles as heroes with the strength of their family bond, while defending Earth from a ravenous space god called Galactus and his enigmatic Herald, Silver Surfer.
title: The Fantastic Four: First Steps
production_companies: Marvel Studios, Kevin Feige Productions

overview: The toys throw Ken and Barbie a Hawaiian vacation in Bonnie's room.
title: Hawaiian Vacation
production_companies: Pixar

overview: Overwhelmed by her suffocating schedule, touring European princess Ann takes off for a night while in Rome. When a sedative she took from her doctor kicks in, however, she falls asleep on a park bench and is found by an American reporter, Joe Bradley, who takes her back to his apartment for safety. At work the next morning, Joe finds out Ann's regal identity and bets his editor he can get exclusive interview with her, but romance soon gets in the way.
title: Roman Holiday
production_companies: Paramount Pictures

overview: One day at work, unsuccessful puppeteer Craig finds a portal into the head of actor John Malkovich. The portal soon becomes a passion for anybody who enters its mad and controlling world of overtaking another human body.
title: Being John Malkovich
production_companies: PolyGram Filmed Entertainment, Propaganda Films, Single Cell Pictures
tagline: Ever wanted to be someone else? Now you can.

overview: On a cold Christmas Eve, selfish miser Ebenezer Scrooge has one night left to face his past — and change the future — before time runs out.
title: Scrooge: A Christmas Carol
production_companies: Timeless Films, Axis Studios

overview: Nicholas Hathaway, a furloughed convict, and his American and Chinese partners hunt a high-level cybercrime network from Chicago to Los Angeles to Hong Kong to Jakarta. As Hathaway closes in, the stakes become personal as he discovers that the attack on a Chinese nuclear power plant was just the beginning.
title: Blackhat
production_companies: Legendary Pictures, Forward Pass
tagline: We are no longer in control.
spoken_languages: Deutsch, English, 广州话 / 廣州話, Español, Bahasa indonesia, Italiano, 普通话

overview: Despite being well into adulthood, brothers Doug and Steve Butabi still live at home and work in the flower shop owned by their dad. They exist only to hit on women at discos, though they're routinely unsuccessful until a chance run-in with Richard Grieco gets them inside the swank Roxbury club. Mistaken for high rollers, they meet their dream women, Vivica and Cambi, and resolve to open a club of their own.
title: A Night at the Roxbury
production_companies: Paramount Pictures, SNL Studios
tagline: Score!

overview: A dangerous CIA renegade resurfaces after a decade on the run. When the safe house he's remanded to is attacked by mercenaries, a rookie operative escapes with him. Now, the unlikely allies must stay alive long enough to uncover who wants them dead.
title: Safe House
production_companies: Universal Pictures, Relativity Media, Bluegrass Films, dentsu
tagline: No one is safe

overview: Despite being well into adulthood, brothers Doug and Steve Butabi still live at home and work in the flower shop owned by their dad. overview: A botched faith healing bestows supernatural Shaman powers on a bullied teenager. When his lifelong tormentors pull a prank that kills someone he loves, he uses his powers for revenge and goes on a bloody rampage to settle the score.
title: The Unhealer
tagline: With great power comes great pain

original_title: Perché quelle strane gocce di sangue sul corpo di Jennifer?
overview: A high-rise apartment populated by models, nightclub dancers and call girls becomes the focus of a mysterious serial killer. When a young model named Jennifer and her friend Marilyn move into one of the victims' former apartments, Jennifer becomes the next target and the pair try to identify the killer.
title: The Case of the Bloody Iris
production_companies: Galassia Cinematografica, Lea Film
tagline: The killer slices without mercy!

overview: After losing their star player, a high school basketball team rooted in Native American culture must unite to keep their state championship dreams alive.
title: Rez Ball
production_companies: Wise Entertainment, Chernin Entertainment, Lake Ellyn Entertainment, The SpringHill Company
tagline: Play fast. Shoot fast. Take your shot.

overview: Researchers on the undersea lab Aquatica have genetically altered the brains of captive sharks to develop a cure for Alzheimer's disease. But there's an unexpected side effect: the sharks got smarter, faster, and more dangerous. After a big storm damages their remote research facility, they must fight for their lives.
title: Deep Blue Sea
production_companies: Riche-Ludwig Productions, Village Roadshow Pictures, Groucho III Film Partnership, Warner Bros. Pictures
tagline: Bigger. Smarter. Faster. Meaner.

overview: A long time ago in a distant fairy tale countryside, a young girl leads her little brother into a dark wood in desperate search of food and work, only to stumble upon a nexus of terrifying evil.
title: Gretel & Hansel
production_companies: Automatik Entertainment, Bron Studios, Creative Wealth Media Finance, Orion Pictures
production_countries: Canada, Ireland, United States of America
tagline: A grim fairy tale

overview: Director James Toback takes an unflinching, uncompromising look at the life of Mike Tyson--almost solely from the perspective of the man himself. TYSON alternates between the controversial boxer addressing the camera and shots of the champion's fights to create an arresting picture of the man.
title: Tyson
production_companies: Wild Bunch, Green Room Films
tagline: The man. The legend. The truth.

overview: Liang Qu is a chic, confident and cold but charming half cat, half human due to a magic spell and he has the ability to melt/heal broken hearts. He lives with Miao Xiao Wan, an honest, confident woman who's created an app that translates cats' sounds and language.
title: Catman

overview: Olaf is on a mission to harness the best holiday traditions for Anna, Elsa, and Kristoff.
title: Olaf's Frozen Adventure
production_companies: Walt Disney Pictures

overview: To prevent a world war from breaking out, famous characters from Victorian literature band together to do battle against a cunning villain.
title: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen
production_companies: 20th Century Fox, Mediastream III, Don Murphy Productions
tagline: The power of seven become a league of one.

overview: A dystopian coming-of-age horror story about three young brothers who live in a cabin in the middle of the woods and hide a dark disturbing secret in their basement.
title: Parvulos
production_companies: Red Elephant, Maligno Gorehouse, Corazón Films
tagline: Family is worth dying for.

overview: A high school swim champion with a troubled past enrolls in the U.S. Coast Guard's 'A' School, where legendary rescue swimmer, Ben Randall teaches him some hard lessons about loss, love, and self-sacrifice.
title: The Guardian
production_companies: Touchstone Pictures, Beacon Pictures, Contrafilm, Firm Films, Eyetronics, A School Productions
tagline: How do you decide who lives or who dies?

overview: Mick Haller is a charismatic defense attorney who does business out of his Lincoln Continental sedan. Mick spends most of his time defending petty crooks and other bottom-feeders, so it comes as quite a surprise when he lands the case of a lifetime: defending a Beverly Hills playboy who is accused of attempted murder. However, what Mick initially thinks is an open-and-shut case with a big monetary reward develops into something more sinister.
title: The Lincoln Lawyer
production_companies: Sidney Kimmel Entertainment, Lionsgate, Lakeshore Entertainment, Stone Village Pictures
tagline: This case is a dangerous game of life and death.

overview: A photographer's obsessive pursuit of dark subject matter leads him into the path of a serial killer who stalks late night commuters, ultimately butchering them in the most gruesome ways.
title: The Midnight Meat Train
production_companies: Lakeshore Entertainment, Lions Gate Films, Midnight Picture Show, GreeneStreet Films
tagline: The most terrifying ride you'll ever take

original_title: NARUTO -ナルト- 滝隠れの死闘 オレが英雄だってばよ!
overview: Naruto and his friends must get back a jug of stolen holy water from a band of higher class ninjas.
title: Naruto: The Lost Story - Mission: Protect the Waterfall Village!
production_companies: Pierrot

overview: Kara and Jessie are two teenage girls from very different worlds, but with a little Christmas magic, they find they have much more in common than they ever imagined.
title: Christmas in the Heartland
production_companies: BCF Film Group, Ascension Media

overview: A sought-after Supercop gets caught in a series of unexpected events when he encounters a suspect who is accused of being involved in a murder case.
title: Vettaiyan
production_companies: Lyca Productions
tagline: The Hunter

original_title: The Return of the Living Dead
overview: When foreman Frank shows new employee Freddy a secret military experiment in a supply warehouse in Louisville, Kentucky, the two klutzes accidentally release a gas that reanimates corpses into flesh-eating zombies. As the epidemic spreads throughout the town, and the creatures satisfy their hunger in gory and outlandish ways, Frank and Freddy fight to survive with the help of their boss and a mysterious mortician.
title: The Return of the Living Dead
production_companies: Hemdale Film Corporation, Fox Films Ltd., Cinema 84, Orion Pictures
production_countries: United Kingdom, United States of America
tagline: They're Back From The Grave and Ready To Party!

overview: A year after losing his friend in a tragic 4,000-foot fall, former ranger Gabe Walker and his partner, Hal, are called to return to the same peak to rescue a group of stranded climbers, only to learn the climbers are actually thieving hijackers who are looking for boxes full of money.
title: Cliffhanger
production_companies: Carolco Pictures, Pioneer, Le Studio Canal+, RCS Video
production_countries: France, Italy, United States of America
tagline: The height of adventure.
